Package edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course.Course

  • public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
    Object containing all the information for a Course within the WolfScheduler program such as: name, title, section, credits, instructorId, meetingDays, startTime, and endTime.
    Author:
    Bilal Mohamad
